  <div class="detail_title">2.	How to pay with credit/debit card</div></div>
<div class="detail">
<!--gai-->
<img src="/style/image/pic/vise.jpg" width="547" height="33" />
<span><p>We currently accept a variety of credit/debit cards including Visa, MasterCard, and American Express. It’s easy to use a credit/debit card to pay for your orders, just do as follows:</p>
<p>1. On your Shopping Cart page, click<img src="/style/image/pic/pay.jpg" width="115" height="24" /> after reviewing your items，fill the shipping information, choose shipping methodsand click</p>
<img src="/style/image/pic/pay.jpg" width="115" height="24" />  once again</p>
<p>2. On the Order Information page, remember your order number and check the amount you need to pay, if everything is all right, you can click<img src="/style/image/pic/pay.jpg" width="115" height="24" /> fill in your card information and just follow it to finish the payment. </p>
<br><div class="centent"><img src="/style/image/pic/country.jpg" width="465" height="222"/> </div>
<img src="/style/image/pic/dingdan.jpg" width="768" height="560" />
<p>3. Once you’ve filled in your payment details, click<img src="/style/image/pic/continue.jpg" width="128" height="32" /> to complete payment for your item(s).
Honeybuy.com does not store or review your credit card & personal information. As such, should any issues arise regarding your credit card or debit card transaction, please contact GlobalCollect or your credit card company for assistance.
</p></span>
